body_html:
@lwogulis : xla_dump_graph* was meant to refer to a set of flags, like xla_dump_hlo_text_to etc. (see the link in my previous comment: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/compiler/xla/legacy_flags/service_flags.cc#L75)

Closing this issue out since it seems that the xla-dev@ mailing list would be a more appropriate forum for XLA (which is still "alpha/experimental") specific questions.
